snippet.title: Pink Takes Shape | Queers Fight Transphobia Marathon 2023 [Part 22]
snippet.description:
Queers Fight Transphobia 2023 was a fundraising event raising money for The Transgender Law Center. This marathon stream was our main contribution to the fundraiser, and it ran for 16 hours on June 24th, 2023. In total, the fundraiser raised $4000 for the Transgender Law Center.

To buy any of the games from this stream, check our collection on Itch.io! https://itch.io/c/3416437/queers-fight-transphobia-2023-marathon

For more GorlStreamTeam, check us out on Twitch! https://www.twitch.tv/gorlstreamteam

Many thanks to everyone who donated to the fundraiser, and big thanks to our collaborators: @Koboltoon, @riversidewings7241, @breakbeatbun, @melodyjettwerner, Fior, and Vera
